comments: Replay review of the shooting foul called on Murray (SAS) pursuant to a coach?s challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Murray (SAS) makes contact with Sabonis' (SAC) arm that affects his shot near the rim.
Sabonis (SAC) makes marginal contact with his forearm to Murray's (SAS) body during his driving shot attempt.
Poeltl (SAS) and Sabonis (SAC) mutually engage during the rebound and the contact is marginal.
DiVincenzo (SAC) makes marginal contact to Walker IV's (SAS) arm during his drive to the basket.
Sabonis (SAC) jumps and makes contact with Walker IV's (SAS) body that affects his driving shot attempt.
Barnes (SAC) and Jones (SAC) both engage with Poeltl (SAS) during the rebound, but do not affect his ability to get to the rebound.
Murray (SAS) briefly holds and releases Lyles (SAC) during the pick but the contact is marginal.
Jones (SAC) reaches in and makes clean contact with the ball during Murray's (SAS) drive and the ensuing contact is incidental.
Jones (SAS) commits a take foul on DiVincenzo (SAC).
Poeltl (SAS) is late to establish himself in a screening position in Barnes' (SAC) path and makes contact that affects his legal guarding position.
Walker IV (SAS) makes contact with two hands to Barnes' (SAC) body that affects his SQBR.
Bates-Diop (SAS) commits a take foul on Barnes (SAC).
